"Guh!": "I commend your efforts. However, they are naught but the efforts of a human vessel."
"Whether dust among the stars, or dust among the earth. Such a difference will always exist between you and the other riffraff."
"Ever since my birth, I have existed for the purpose of ruling the world. I am its vessel, after all."
"Existing just to rule the world... What a load of crap...!"
"This is...! The ARKS Ship autonomy code?! But why... it couldn't be!"
